@ Test
public class TestBeanQuery {
public void
test_simple () {
Address
address =
new
Address ()
;
address. setStreet
(
"Broadway"
)
;
BeanQuery <
String
>
bq1 =
address. street
()
.
metaProperty ()
;
assertEquals (
bq1. get
(
address
)
,
"Broadway"
)
;
BeanQuery <
String
>
bq2 =
address. metaBean
()
.
street ()
;
assertEquals (
bq2. get
(
address
)
,
"Broadway"
)
;
}
//-------------------------------------------------------------------------
public void
test_chained () {
Address
address =
new
Address ()
;
address. setOwner
(
new
Person ()
)
;
address. getOwner
()
.
setSurname (
"Joda"
)
;
ChainedBeanQuery <
String
>
bq =
ChainedBeanQuery. of
(
Address. meta
()
.
owner ()
,
Person. meta
()
.
surname ()
)
;
assertEquals (
bq. get
(
address
)
,
"Joda"
)
;
}
